      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·甫田之什·006.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鴛鴦.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鴛鴦于飛，畢之羅之。君子萬年，福祿宜之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Yellow ducks fly about,
And are taken with hand-nets and spread-nets.
May our sovereign live for ten thousand years,
Enjoying the happiness and wealth which are his due!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
