      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鴛鴦.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鴛鴦在梁，戢其左翼。君子萬年，宜其遐福。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Yellow ducks are on the dam,
With their left wings gathered up.
May our sovereign live for ten thousand years,
Enjoying the happiness and wealth which are his due!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
