      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鴛鴦.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>乘馬在廏，摧之秣之。君子萬年，福祿艾之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The teams of steeds are in the stable,
Fed with forage and grain.
May our sovereign live for ten thousand years,
Sustained in his happiness and wealth!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
